nvtop (3.2.0.2-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add arm64 builds with GitHub Actions (deb, rpm and AppImage)
  * Add arm64, armhf, i386, powerpc, ppc64el, riscv64, s390x builds to PPA
  * Fix build no longer included in PPA publishing (rely on CMake to install bin and assets)
  * Build type as release & use CMake instead of make
  * Bump versions to oldest supported in workflows
  * Add GitHub Action job to build on other distros of Ubuntu or Debian (previous or not LTS versions, minimum is focal or bullseye)

 -- Quentin Lienhardt <pro@quentium.fr>  Tue, 14 Aug 2025 18:00:00 +0100

